          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Elif Armagan, the TikToker in question, not only was featured in the Bring A Trailer Instagram account’s profile photo, her likeness was used in 12 successive posts during the 24-hour period. A link to the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
